snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom – Announcement Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
It's up to Princess Zelda to save Hyrule in a brand-new The Legend of Zelda adventure. 

The Legend of Zelda: Echoes of Wisdom launches September 26th on Nintendo Switch!

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun: https://goo.gl/HYYsot
